NAME
	llm-context (display) - render one horizontal fill bar per session id listed in an index file, with a watermark tick at the historical maximum

INTERFACE
	display (MatrixDisplay)

READS
	sessions	one numeric session id per line
	<id>/current	single line: ms model tokens limit
	<id>/history	lines "ms tokens limit"; only the max tokens
			value is used, as the watermark

WRITES
	none (renders only)

DESCRIPTION
	One 36 px row per session: model name, tokens/limit readout, fill
	bar proportional to tokens/limit, watermark tick at the history
	maximum.  Re-reads on every update tick.  No pointer or key
	handling.

SEE ALSO
	llm-recorder (produces this input tree)
